                  <T>0xEA115F6<!--I've noticed those little green fellas over by the swing sets in Crow's Crossing, and I've also noticed that a couple houses elsewhere here seem to have a lot going on. I'm dying, practically <i>dying</i>, to spend time in haunted places.--></T>
                </L>
